84fd5baf91df91889cfcfed2bcf59f073dc754f6aba1944059203bbe99f4bbb6dc92addff9fae8f687a2c95f9438b0eb301dd0320728a8a2a6edd5e2b2b5ba94  musl-bswap.patch"
